@startuml
' Scope: lesson completion and monthly billing projection
' Related: UC-08, UC-09, FR-LSN-01, BR-LSN-01, FR-BIL-01, BR-BIL-01
title 授業完了・月次請求 シーケンス図
autonumber

actor "先生" as Teacher
participant "completeLesson\nServer Action" as Complete
participant "Billing page\nServer Component" as Billing
participant "billing helper" as Calculator
participant "payment actions" as Payment
participant "NextAuth auth()" as Auth
database "PostgreSQL\nPrisma" as DB

Teacher -> Complete : lessonIdを完了確定
Complete -> Auth : teacher roleを確認
Auth --> Complete : teacherId
Complete -> DB : id + teacherId + completedAt=nullを検索
Complete -> DB : completedAtを現在時刻へ更新
Complete --> Teacher : カレンダーを再検証

Teacher -> Billing : year / monthを指定して表示
Billing -> Auth : teacher roleを確認
Billing -> DB : teacherId + 月範囲 + completedAt!=nullで授業取得
loop 完了授業ごと
  Billing -> Calculator : durationMin, hourlyRate, travelExpense
  Calculator --> Billing : lessonFee + total
end
Billing -> DB : teacherId + studentId + year + monthの支払状態取得
Billing --> Teacher : 生徒別内訳・合計・入金状態

Teacher -> Payment : 入金、未入金、期限を更新
Payment -> Auth : teacher roleを確認
Payment -> DB : studentId + teacherIdの所有確認
Payment -> DB : MonthlyPaymentをupsert / delete
Payment --> Teacher : /billingを再検証

note over Billing,DB
  未完了授業は請求に含めない。
  すべての集計と支払状態をteacherIdで分離する。
end note
@enduml

